    "body": "PR create https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/pull/13002\r\n\r\nHost can change Team and Spawn of any player to make it simpler and quicker to setup new game.\r\nAdapted for all our mods. New mods will also have this feature. Existing external mods with custom lobby_players screen will keep current functionality (Team and Spawn readonly for Host), but they can simply adapt it to support this feature.\r\n\r\nSoScared's initial idea isn't clear for me, I assume it would be harder."
